body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.  
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of personal information.  
Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand.
The conversation should be at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time and end the conversation.
Return the conversation formatted like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Good morning! My name is Philip Robinson and I am with Prestige Car Rentals. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Tammy Jenkins.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Ms. Jenkins. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm having some trouble with the return process for my rental car. I wanted to discuss the steps.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'd be happy to assist with that. For verification purposes, can I please have your rental agreement number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's zero one two three four five six.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. Also, for our records, could I have the make and model of the vehicle you rented?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for providing that information. I have all the details here. To solve your issue, I...

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your patience, Ms. Jenkins. Your return process issue has been resolved. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. Thank you so much for your help!

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further assistance in the future, feel free to contact us. Thank you for choosing Prestige Car Rentals, and have a great day!
